room_title: Escape room "Mad Lab: Resurrection" by Great Room Escape San Diego in San Diego
room_description: Join the Mad Scientist in a frantic quest to resurrect the chained up, radioactive Professor and break into the vault! There you will find valuable assets and key information needed while the triggered alarm in counting down 60 minutes to complete annihilation of the lab! Will you be able to escape before the clock hits zero?
